---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import site from "../content/site/settings.json";
---

<Base
  title="Mary Jane's Place — Britain's first patient sanctuary for prescribed medical cannabis"
  description="Mary Jane's Place is Britain's first patient sanctuary for prescribed medical cannabis. Flagship in Bournemouth, with a UK-wide network in development. Trusted information, lawful safe space, prestige membership."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-copy">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">Britain's first patient sanctuary · Flagship · Bournemouth</div>
      <h1 class="rv">Where medical cannabis patients belong.</h1>
      <p class="sub rv">
        Mary Jane's Place is Britain's first dedicated sanctuary for prescribed medical cannabis
        patients — a safe, dignified space to use your medicine, with the information, community
        and legal backing to do so confidently. Built by a patient, going national.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta rv">
        <a class="btn" href="/membership">See membership <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/medical-cannabis">Medical cannabis, explained</a>
      </div>
      <div class="reassure rv">
        <span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg> Legal since 2018</span>
        <span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg> Prescription required</span>
        <span><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg> Vaporisers only · 18+</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad">
    <div class="wrap two vc">
      <div class="rv">
        <div class="eyebrow kick">The white space</div>
        <h2>The UK has clinics. We're the place patients go after.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="rv">
        <p style="margin-bottom:14px">
          Britain's medical cannabis clinics — Releaf, Mamedica, Curaleaf and the rest — are
          excellent at prescribing. There are over 150,000 prescribed patients in the UK today,
          a number that doubled in 2025 alone. Yet most are still asked to leave venues for
          using legal medicine.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mary Jane's Place exists for the rest of the journey: a verified, vaporiser-only
          sanctuary where the prescription you've worked for can actually be used. Calmly,
          lawfully, and without explaining yourself.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">How membership works</div>
      <div class="steps" style="margin-top:12px">
        <div class="step rv">
          <div class="n">STEP ONE</div>
          <h3>Hold a prescription</h3>
          <p>You have a valid UK prescription from a registered specialist clinician.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step rv">
          <div class="n">STEP TWO</div>
          <h3>Get verified</h3>
          <p>Show photo ID and proof of prescription (within six months) once. Done.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step rv">
          <div class="n">STEP THREE</div>
          <h3>You're a member</h3>
          <p>Use the sanctuary, join the community, choose a tier when you're ready.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rv" style="margin-top:18px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <a class="btn" href="/membership">Compare tiers <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/visit">Plan a visit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">Start here</div>
      <h2 class="rv" style="margin-bottom:24px">Clear, honest, properly sourced.</h2>
      <div class="three">
        <a class="navcard rv" href="/medical-cannabis">
          <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M9 3h6v4l4 14H5L9 7z"/><path d="M9 13h6"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Medical Cannabis</h3>
          <p>What it is, who can be prescribed it, how patients use it. Plain English, citations included.</p>
          <span class="go">Read more →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="navcard rv" href="/your-rights">
          <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Your Rights</h3>
          <p>UK law sources directly cited. NPCC police guidance, Equality Act, Road Traffic Act and more.</p>
          <span class="go">Read more →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="navcard rv" href="/blog">
          <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h12"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Patient blog</h3>
          <p>Guides, news and how-tos written for prescribed UK patients. Updated regularly.</p>
          <span class="go">Read more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="band rv">
        <div class="facts">
          {site.facts.map((f) => (
            <div class="fact">
              <div class="big">{f.value}</div>
              <div class="lbl">{f.label}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p style="text-align:center;margin-top:28px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);font-size:12.5px">
          Patient numbers from CQC controlled-drug reporting and Business of Cannabis market analysis, 2025–26.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap narrow center">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">The plan</div>
      <h2 class="rv">One sanctuary today. More to come.</h2>
      <p class="rv" style="margin-top:14px">
        We're starting in Bournemouth because that's where the founder lives, was prescribed,
        and was asked to leave. The ambition is to grow Mary Jane's Place into trusted
        sanctuaries across the UK, so every patient — wherever they live — has somewhere to go,
        and somewhere to belong. If you'd like to help bring one to your city,
        <a class="tlink" href="/partnerships">we'd like to talk</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="rv" style="margin-top:22px">
        <a class="btn" href="/membership">See membership <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
